social_posts.post_text: Cuddle buddies for life!!! Yup, we signed a contract. In perpetuity. @caricosta

Happy 21st Birthday Anna Banana! What a pleasure it’s been watching you grow from the timid bookworm that would steal my clothes, into this exuberant, hilarious, and responsible woman who now asks to borrow my clothes. Love you so much!

Apparently, I can’t be trusted behind the wheel and I would be VERY insulted were it not for the fact that @trims440 is the most badass stunt driver in the game. Swipe right to see that it’s not our first rodeo together.
We ended up on Santa’s lap (which he won’t remember because he’s obviously drunk). Pretty sure he liked it. Pretty sure our kids are getting the best gifts this year. @angelbekoff

There was tea and there was THE tea! Loved celebrating your beautiful, crazy ass! @caricosta ❤️❤️❤️
@caricosta @zoe.winkler.reinis @denisevasi @hannahskvarla @kuenyc nataliegweiner @iammarlendavis

When you never get out and you steal away to Miami for two nights, you obviously make a music video out of it. Told you it was coming @angelbekoff !! Thank you guys for making it the best New Years yet!!! Love the shit out of you two!!!! ❤️❤️❤️

Disneyland around Christmastime is magical on a whole different level. She’ll look back and remember today as being the best day ever. And by she, I of course mean @angelbekoff 😆 Four-year-olds don’t remember shit! 🥴
@disneyland

“Love is the one thing that transcends time and space.”
Happy Birthday, big sister.💜

Healthy again. Took a minute, though. 🥴
Thank you @lamodelsdirect for my new digitals! 😘

Happiest of Birthdays @angelbekoff !!! The Angel to my Cherub. What would I do without you? When you strolled into my life 16 years ago as Matt’s plus one, you quickly made Matt the plus one (Love how he still whines about it😂). Thank you for loving my kids like your own. For always taking my side in an argument against Matt, even when I’m wrong. Thank you for talking me off the ledge (multiple times) and trying to convince me to NOT leave the house at 5am (I should’ve listened) but mostly, thank you for being exactly who you are, all the time- honest, loving, kind, the best listener, and a cheerleader to each and every one of your friends, not to mention the best amateur interior designer! I’m so lucky to call you a best friend. Enjoy this day and every day because you fucking deserve all the wonderful-ness!!! Love you sooooo much! ❤️❤️❤️

Fine. If you insist on showing them a picture, stop scrolling and just show them this. 😆😘 🔥🔥
